=== 示威與鎮壓（2011年1月－7月） ===
{{參見|叙利亚内战年表 (2011年1月－2011年4月)|叙利亚内战年表 (2011年5月－2011年8月)}}
2011年3月15日在首都[[大馬士革|大馬士革]]發生了大型的示威活動，抗議者要求民主改革和釋放政治犯。政府對抗議者開火<ref name="SCW" />，並且有多人被羈押。<ref>{{Cite web |title=Mid-East unrest: Syrian protests in Damascus and Aleppo |url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-12749674 |accessdate=2015-08-07 |publisher=BBC |archive-date=2016-07-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160721131547/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-12749674 |dead-url=no }}</ref>此次抗議活動是由一群孩童在月初被政府逮捕所引起，他們在[[德拉|德拉]]的牆上留下“人民希望政權倒台”塗鴉。<ref name="SCW">{{Cite news |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2013/02/09/world/middleeast/a-faceless-teenage-refugee-who-helped-ignite-syrias-war.html?_r=1 |title=A Faceless Teenage Refugee Who Helped Ignite Syria's War |first=Kareem |date=2013-02-08 |publisher=New York Times |last2=Saad |first2=Hwaida |accessdate=2015-08-07 |last1=Fahim |archive-date=2016-02-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160201135116/http://www.nytimes.com/2013/02/09/world/middleeast/a-faceless-teenage-refugee-who-helped-ignite-syrias-war.html?_r=1 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="DR">{{Cite web |title=Middle East unrest: Silence broken in Syria |url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-12794882 |accessdate=2015-08-07 |publisher=BBC |archive-date=2016-07-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160721131551/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-12794882 |dead-url=no }}</ref>在鎮壓之後，3月18日的星期五（「尊嚴星期五」）全國各地爆發更大規模的示威活動。20日，示威者燒毀了一棟復興黨黨部和“其他建築物”。隨後的衝突造成7名警察<ref>{{Cite web |title=Syria: Seven Police Killed, Buildings Torched in Protests |url=http://www.israelnationalnews.com/News/News.aspx/143026#.VdOFupexlmE |accessdate=2015-08-18 |publisher=Israel National News |archive-date=2019-05-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190515002936/http://www.israelnationalnews.com/News/News.aspx/143026#.VdOFupexlmE |dead-url=no }}</ref>和15名抗議者喪生。<ref>{{Cite web |title=The struggle for Syria in 2011 |url=http://www.understandingwar.org/sites/default/files/Struggle_For_Syria.pdf |accessdate=2015-08-07 |publisher=Understanding War |archive-date=2019-04-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190430184640/http://www.understandingwar.org/sites/default/files/Struggle_For_Syria.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>十天後的一次講話中，總統[[巴沙爾·阿薩德|巴沙爾·阿薩德]]譴責“外國陰謀”，指控[[以色列|以色列]]為抗議活動宣傳。<ref>{{Cite web |title=Assad blames conspirators for Syrian protests |url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2011/mar/30/syrian-protests-assad-blames-conspirators |accessdate=2015-08-07 |publisher=The Guardian |archive-date=2015-07-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150713162127/http://www.theguardian.com/world/2011/mar/30/syrian-protests-assad-blames-conspirators |dead-url=no }}</ref>

示威活動在全國蔓延，4月1日的星期五（「烈士星期五」）有超過25萬人參加，4月8日的星期五（「反抗星期五」）抗議活動同時出現在十大城市，4月22日的星期五（「偉大星期五」）有二十座城市發生抗議活動。在4月7日前，抗議者的訴求主要是民主改革，釋放政治犯，更多的自由，廢除緊急狀態法，終結貪腐。但4月8日之後，示威口號的重點逐漸轉成推翻阿薩德政府。4月25日，敘利亞軍隊開始在相關城市進行大規模的鎮壓，使用了坦克、步兵戰鬥車和砲兵，導致數百名平民死亡。至5月底，共有1,000名平民<ref name="bbc24M11">{{Cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-13529923 |title=US policy on Syria 'depends on success in Libya' |date=2011-05-24 |publisher=BBC |accessdate=2014-03-07 |archive-date=2018-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181121012437/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-13529923 |dead-url=no }}</ref>、150名士兵和警察<ref name="Kh.31-5-11">{{Cite news |url=http://www.khaleejtimes.com/DisplayArticle09.asp?xfile=data/middleeast/2011/May/middleeast_May870.xml&section=middleeast |title=Armed residents put up resistance to Syrian army |date=2011-05-31 |newspaper=Khaleej Times (Dubai) |accessdate=2014-04-02 |archive-date=2013-04-07 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6FhyYcNNz?url=http://www.khaleejtimes.com/DisplayArticle09.asp?xfile=data%2Fmiddleeast%2F2011%2FMay%2Fmiddleeast_May870.xml |dead-url=no }}</ref>被打死，數千人被拘留<ref name=bbc5511,17.19GMT>{{Cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-13299793 |title=Syria protests: Rights group warns of 'Deraa massacre' |date=2011-05-05<!-- 17:19GMT --> |publisher=BBC |accessdate=2014-02-02 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110506035755/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-13299793 |archivedate=2011-05-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref>；被捕者當中有很多學生、自由派人士和人權倡導者。<ref>{{Cite web |title=From Jail to Jihad: Former Prisoners Fight in Syrian Insurgency |url=http://www.spiegel.de/international/world/former-prisoners-fight-in-syrian-insurgency-a-927158.html |accessdate=2014-05-27 |date=2013-10-10 |last=Salloum |first=Raniah |work=Spiegel |archive-date=2014-06-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140606234654/http://www.spiegel.de/international/world/former-prisoners-fight-in-syrian-insurgency-a-927158.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

明顯對抗政府的武裝起事開始於[[伊德利卜省|伊德利卜省]]，靠近土耳其的邊境城市[[吉斯爾舒古爾|吉斯爾舒古爾]]，6月4日安全部隊對葬禮遊行隊伍開槍後，哀悼者放火焚燒建築物，造成8名安全人員死亡，並且佔領一間警察局，奪取武器。隨後的日子，暴力持續升級。有未經證實的報導稱[[吉斯爾舒古爾|吉斯爾舒古爾]]的安全部隊有一部分叛變，之後秘密警察和情報人員處決拒絕對平民開槍的士兵。<ref name="autogenerated5">{{Cite journal |title=The Struggle for Syria in 2011 |author=Holliday, Joseph |url=http://www.understandingwar.org/sites/default/files/Struggle_For_Syria.pdf |date=December 2011 |journal=Institute for the Study of War |accessdate=2013-09-20 |archive-date=2019-04-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190430184640/http://www.understandingwar.org/sites/default/files/Struggle_For_Syria.pdf |dead-url=no }} (page 21)</ref>後來，更多的敘利亞示威者拿起武器，也有更多的士兵投靠保護示威者。

衝突中，政府和民眾雙方都以宣傳來鞏固他們的論述，並詆毀對方。至2011年7月底，約有1,600名平民和500名安全部隊被殺害，13,000人遭逮捕。

=== 起事（2011年7月－10月） ===
{{參見|叙利亚内战年表 (2011年5月－2011年8月)|叙利亚内战年表 (2011年9月－2011年12月)}}

2011年7月29日，吉迅成立[[敘利亞自由軍|敘利亞自由軍]]，成員包括前敘利亞武裝部隊的軍官和士兵，目標為聯合反對力量“推翻政權（阿薩德政府）”。<ref name="Landis29-7-11">{{Cite web |title=Free Syrian Army Founded by Seven Officers to Fight the Syrian Army |url=http://www.joshualandis.com/blog/?p=11043 |accessdate=2014-05-29 |date=2011-07-29 |last=Landis |first=Joshua |publisher=Syria Comment |archive-date=2012-07-23 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/69NZHSDi5?url=http://www.joshualandis.com/blog/?p=11043 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="wtarc">{{Cite news |url=http://www.worldtribune.com/worldtribune/WTARC/2011/me_syria0973_08_03.asp |title=Defecting troops form 'Free Syrian Army', target Assad security forces |date=2011-08-03 |accessdate=2014-05-29 |agency=World Tribune |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111127210252/http://www.worldtribune.com/worldtribune/WTARC/2011/me_syria0973_08_03.asp |archivedate=2011-11-27 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>7月31日，被稱為“齋月大屠殺（Ramadan Massacre）”的全國性鎮壓造成至少142人死亡及數百人受傷。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.dawn.com/news/648303/syrian-army-kills-at-least-95-in-hama-activist |title=Syrian army kills at least 95 in Hama: activist |date=2011-07-31 |work=Dawn |accessdate=2015-06-07 |agency=Agence France-Presse |archive-date=2018-05-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180530142715/https://www.dawn.com/news/648303/syrian-army-kills-at-least-95-in-hama-activist |dead-url=no }}</ref>8月23日，反政府的組織聯合組成[[敘利亞全國委員會|敘利亞全國委員會]]。總部設在土耳其，試圖組織反對運動。然而，這個包括自由軍等各個政治團體的聯盟並不是很穩定，流亡人士、草根組織者和武裝分子因為意識形態、種族和宗派線分隔成許多派別。<ref name="NYT Topic: Syria">{{Cite news |url=http://topics.nytimes.com/top/news/international/countriesandterritories/syria/index.html |title=Syria News |first=Anne |work=The New York Times |last2=Hubbard |first2=Ben |accessdate=2012-08-02 |last1=Barnard |archive-date=2011-05-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110511141803/http://topics.nytimes.com/top/news/international/countriesandterritories/syria/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>整個8月，敘利亞部隊突襲各大主要城市和邊境，並繼續鎮壓抗議活動。8月底的[[開齋節|開齋節]]慶典被禁止後，安全部隊對示威者聚集的[[霍姆斯_(敘利亞)|霍姆斯]]、[[德拉|德拉]]、[[大馬士革|大馬士革]]郊區發動攻擊。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.alarabiya.net/articles/2011/08/30/164705.html |title=Syrian forces kill seven protesters as Muslims celebrate first day of Eid |date=2011-08-30 |publisher=Al Arabiya |accessdate=2012-02-01 |dead-url=yes |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180617165232/https://www.alarabiya.net/articles/2011/08/30/164705.html |archive-date=2018-06-17 }}</ref>

2011年9月，敘利亞反政府武裝組織在各地積極開展叛亂活動。[[自由敘利亞軍|自由敘利亞軍]]和政府軍之間主要的衝突發生在[[拉斯坦|拉斯坦]]。從9月27日至10月1日，政府軍在坦克和直升機的支援下，對[[霍姆斯省|霍姆斯省]]的拉斯坦發動大規模攻勢，以驅除叛軍。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/09/27/syria-town-idUSL5E7KR02A20110927 |title=Syria forces storm main town, fight defectors-residents |date=2011-09-27 |agency=Reuters |accessdate=2015-10-17 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924155425/http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/09/27/syria-town-idUSL5E7KR02A20110927 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>2011年的拉斯坦戰役是那時政府軍與自由軍最激烈與最長的戰鬥。一個星期後，自由軍被迫從拉斯坦撤退。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-13988701 |title=Syria: 'Hundreds of thousands' join anti-Assad protests |date=2011-07-01 |publisher=BBC |accessdate=2011-08-03 |archive-date=2011-08-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110805061523/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-13988701 |dead-url=no }}</ref>為了躲避政府圍剿，自由軍的領導人上校[[里亞德·阿薩德|里亞德·阿薩德]]撤退到土耳其。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/10/04/us-syria-opposition-idUSL5E7L41CT20111004 |title=Dissident Syrian colonel flees to Turkey |last=Oweis |first=Khaled Yacoub |date=2011-10-04 |accessdate=2012-08-18 |agency=Reuters |archive-date=2011-10-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111005183430/http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/10/04/us-syria-opposition-idUSL5E7L41CT20111004 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>許多武裝分子逃到了附近的城市[[霍姆斯_(敘利亞)|霍姆斯]]。

到10月，雙方交戰一直持續。自由軍則開始受到[[土耳其|土耳其]]的積極援助，可以在土國南部[[哈塔伊省|哈塔伊省]]靠近邊境的地區指揮和組織司令部。<ref name="Rebel groups">{{Cite news |url=http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/syrian-rebels-too-fragmented-unruly.aspx?pageID=238&nID=29158&NewsCatID=352 |title=Syrian rebels: Too fragmented, unruly |last=Yezdani |first=İpek |date=2012-09-01 |work=Hürriyet Daily News |accessdate=2012-09-21 |archive-date=2017-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019181343/http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/syrian-rebels-too-fragmented-unruly.aspx?pageID=238&nID=29158&NewsCatID=352 |dead-url=no }}</ref>自由軍利用土敘邊境為安全區和補給線，對敘利亞北部發動攻擊。有叛逃者指出，2011年敘利亞政府有意地釋放關押的伊斯蘭武裝分子，並為他們提供武器，“為了使自己在國際社會中是沒那麼壞的選擇。”<ref>{{Cite web |title=Assad regime set free extremists from prison to fire up trouble during peaceful uprising |url=http://www.thenational.ae/world/syria/assad-regime-set-free-extremists-from-prison-to-fire-up-trouble-during-peaceful-uprising |accessdate=2014-08-11 |date=2014-01-21 |work=The National |last1=Sands |first1=Phil |last2=Vela |first2=Justin |last3=Maayeh |first3=Suha |archive-date=2014-07-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140730012530/http://www.thenational.ae/world/syria/assad-regime-set-free-extremists-from-prison-to-fire-up-trouble-during-peaceful-uprising |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Weiss">{{Cite web |title=Trust Iran Only as Far as You Can Throw It |url=http://www.foreignpolicy.com/articles/2014/06/23/iran_is_funding_isis_syria_iraq_proxy_war |accessdate=2014-08-11 |date=2014-06-23 |last=Weiss |first=Michael |work=Foreign Policy |archive-date=2014-08-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140813003037/http://www.foreignpolicy.com/articles/2014/06/23/iran_is_funding_isis_syria_iraq_proxy_war |dead-url=no }}</ref>

