=== 叙利亚库尔德人 ===
{{主條目|罗贾瓦冲突|库尔德人}}

[[庫德族|庫德族]]主要是[[遜尼派|遜尼派]]穆斯林，另有少數[[雅兹迪|雅兹迪]]教派。2011年起事開始時總共佔敘利亞總人口的10％。他們數十年來受到歧視和忽略，被剝奪基本的公民、文化、經濟和社會權<ref name="OHCHR Sep11">{{Cite journal |title=Report of the United Nations High Commissioner for Human Rights on the situation of human rights in the Syrian Arab Republic |url=http://www.ohchr.org/Documents/countries/SY/Syria_Report_2011-08-17.pdf |date=2011-09-15 |publisher=UN Human Rights Council |accessdate=2012-06-30 |journal= |archive-date=2019-04-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190430071959/https://www.ohchr.org/Documents/countries/SY/Syria_Report_2011-08-17.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在抗爭運動開始後[[阿薩德|阿薩德]]政府最終給予約200,000無國籍的庫德族公民身分，嘗試安撫潛在的庫德族反對派<ref name="HRW Kurds">{{Cite web |title=Syrian Kurds Fleeing to Iraqi Safe Haven |url=http://www.hrw.org/news/2012/05/14/syrian-kurds-fleeing-iraqi-safe-haven |accessdate=2012-06-30 |date=2012-05-14 |last=Muscati |first=Samer |publisher=Human Rights Watch |archive-date=2012-07-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120721212808/http://www.hrw.org/news/2012/05/14/syrian-kurds-fleeing-iraqi-safe-haven |dead-url=no }}</ref>。這個讓步加上許多反對派是由[[土耳其|土耳其]]所支持，以及庫德族在[[敘利亞全國委員會|敘利亞全國委員會]]的代表不足，導致庫德族與敘利亞遜尼派一同參與內戰的人數並不多<ref name="HRW Kurds" />，因此庫德地區的暴力衝突已經降低<ref name="HRW Kurds" />。在後阿薩德時代，庫德族希望能有一個分離的州可以享有高度自治<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://uk.reuters.com/article/2012/07/04/uk-syria-crisis-rifts-idUKBRE8630IY20120704 |title=Syria opposition rifts give world excuse not to act |first=Edmund |date=2012-07-04 |last2=Saleh |first2=Yasmine |accessdate=2012-07-09 |agency=Reuters |last1=Blair |archive-date=2012-10-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121012064350/http://uk.reuters.com/article/2012/07/04/uk-syria-crisis-rifts-idUKBRE8630IY20120704 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

內戰剛開始時，大多數庫德政黨組織起來進入[[爭取民主變革力量全國協調委員會|爭取民主變革力量全國協調委員會]]，對於阿薩德政府的立場相對比較溫和。然而在2011年10月，[[民主联盟党_(叙利亚)|民主聯盟黨]]離開争取民主变革力量全国协调委员会，另外成立[[庫德全國委員會|庫德全國委員會]]。

敘利亞庫德族的[[人民保护部队|人民保护部队]]自2012年7月加入內戰，驅逐了駐守[[科巴尼|科巴尼]]的敘利亞政府軍。庫德族驅逐[[艾因角|艾因角]]的[[阿拉伯人|阿拉伯人]]之後，YPG也與一些伊斯蘭武裝，如[[努斯拉陣線|努斯拉陣線]]之間有衝突<ref>[http://rudaw.net/english/interview/22072013 YPG Commander: Kurds Are Bulwark Against Islamic Extremism in Syria] {{Wayback|url=http://rudaw.net/english/interview/22072013 |date=20150713012336 }}. Rudaw.net.</ref>。2014年[[伊斯蘭國|伊斯蘭國]]興起後入侵[[羅賈瓦|羅賈瓦]]，攻佔了350個庫德村莊和城鎮<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.ibtimes.com/turkeys-parliament-approves-military-action-against-isis-syria-iraq-1698537 |title=Turkey's Parliament Approves Military Action Against ISIS In Syria, Iraq |date=2014-10-02 |publisher=International Business Times |accessdate=2015-10-22 |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303233802/http://www.ibtimes.com/turkeys-parliament-approves-military-action-against-isis-syria-iraq-1698537 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，約有300,000庫德族人逃往[[土耳其|土耳其]]。其中連[[科巴尼之戰|科巴尼]]也一度危急，一直到以[[美國|美國]]為首的聯軍空襲支援以及[[伊拉克庫德斯坦|伊拉克庫德人]]借道土耳其增援抵達後才擊退伊斯蘭國。

=== 伊斯蘭國 ===
{{主条目|伊斯蘭国}}

“伊斯蘭國”（前稱“伊拉克和黎凡特伊斯兰国”）是一个源自[[基地组织|基地组织]]的极端组织，这一组织打算消除在[[第一次世界大战|第一次世界大战]]结束后由協約國勾畫的现代中东的国家边界，并在这一地区创立一个[[政教合一|政教合一]]的伊斯兰[[酋长国|酋长国]]。“伊斯蘭國”的[[恐怖分子|恐怖分子]]们在[[叙利亚|叙利亚]]和[[伊拉克|伊拉克]]实施了造成大量死伤的多重暴力活动。

2013年前该组织称为“伊拉克伊斯兰国”；2013年4月9日宣布与基地组织分支“[[努斯拉阵线|努斯拉阵线]]”合併，称为“伊拉克和沙姆伊斯兰国”。努斯拉阵线拒絕合并，与伊斯蘭國分道扬镳，基地组织于2014年2月宣布与伊拉克和沙姆伊斯兰国决裂。後者於2014年6月攻陷伊拉克北部大城[[摩蘇爾|摩蘇爾]]後，改名「伊斯蘭國」。

除了来自[[伊拉克|伊拉克]]和[[叙利亚|叙利亚]]的成员以外，这个组织也吸引了来自全球81个国家的超过12,000名[[圣战者|圣战者]]加入。他们主要经由[[土耳其|土耳其]]边境进入叙利亚和伊拉克<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.presstv.ir/detail/2014/09/13/378612/isil-using-turkey-territory-to-enter-iraq/ |title=Footage shows ISIL using Turkey to enter Iraq, Syria |date=2014-09-13 |publisher=PressTV |accessdate=2014-10-20 |language=en |archive-date=2014-09-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140920130531/http://www.presstv.ir/detail/2014/09/13/378612/isil-using-turkey-territory-to-enter-iraq/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在[[土耳其|土耳其]]境内位于[[阿达纳省|阿达纳省]]因斯里克空军基地附近，有个专门为[[圣战者|圣战者]]提供训练的训练营。数千名圣战者已完成训练并进入[[叙利亚|叙利亚]]和[[伊拉克|伊拉克]]协助伊斯兰国建立[[伊斯兰国_(政权形式)|伊斯蘭國]]<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.wnd.com/2014/06/source-besieged-iraq-sees-obama-as-jihad-accomplice/ |title=Source: Besieged Iraq sees Obama as jihad 'accomplice' |date=2014-06-16 |publisher=WorldNetDaily |accessdate=2014-10-21 |language=en |archive-date=2014-10-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141011032847/http://www.wnd.com/2014/06/source-besieged-iraq-sees-obama-as-jihad-accomplice/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2014年10月2日[[乔·拜登|美国副总统乔·拜登]]指责[[土耳其|土耳其]]资助伊斯兰国。土耳其否认了这个指责并要求乔·拜登道歉。其实土耳其想借助伊斯蘭國对付[[库德族|库尔德族武装]]和阿薩德政府并不是什么秘密。2012年年初或更早，[[美国中情局|美国中情局]]在[[约旦|约旦]]设立训练营为[[叙利亚反对派|叙利亚反对派]]提供军事训练，多名完成训练的叙反对派成员因受伊斯蘭國理念所吸引，结果加入了该组织<ref name="USAinJordan_FSA2ISIS">{{Cite news |url=http://www.wnd.com/2014/06/officials-u-s-trained-isis-at-secret-base-in-jordan/ |title=Blowback! U.S. trained Islamists who joined ISIS |date=2014-06-17 |publisher=WorldNetDaily |accessdate=2014-10-21 |language=en |archive-date=2014-10-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141020161041/http://www.wnd.com/2014/06/officials-u-s-trained-isis-at-secret-base-in-jordan/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2014年6月[[美国|美国]]向在伊斯蘭國[[叙利亚|叙利亚]]占领区内的难民提供[[人道援助|人道援助]]<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2014/10/19/u-s-humanitarian-aid-going-to-isis.html |title=U.S. Humanitarian Aid Going to ISIS |date=2014-10-19 |publisher=The Daily Beast |accessdate=2014-11-08 |language=en |archive-date=2014-11-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141106164838/http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2014/10/19/u-s-humanitarian-aid-going-to-isis.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 以色列 ===
[[以色列|以色列]]在叙利亚战争中一直和叙利亚政府军敌对。以色列不止数次轰炸和空袭叙利亚的军事目标，还为数个反对派和征服軍武装组织提供创伤治疗和军事培训。<ref name="rt360690">{{Cite news |url=https://www.rt.com/news/360690-us-arms-nusra-syria/ |date=2016-09-26 |publisher=rt.com |script-title=en:‘Americans are on our side’: Al-Nusra commander says US arming jihadists via 3rd countries |accessdate=2016-12-23 |archive-date=2016-12-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161223201229/https://www.rt.com/news/360690-us-arms-nusra-syria/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="israeltreatqaeda">{{Cite news |url=http://www.jpost.com/Middle-East/Report-Israel-treating-al-Qaida-fighters-wounded-in-Syria-civil-war-393862 |title=Report: Israel treating al-Qaida fighters wounded in Syria civil war |date=2015-03-13 |publisher=The Jerusalem Post |accessdate=2017-01-19 |archive-date=2019-05-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190513042444/https://www.jpost.com/Middle-East/Report-Israel-treating-al-Qaida-fighters-wounded-in-Syria-civil-war-393862 |dead-url=no }}</ref>此外，联合国报告指以色列和[[伊斯蘭國|伊斯蘭國]]之间也有定期联系。<ref name="ibtUNisraelisis">{{Cite news |url=http://www.ibtimes.co.in/un-report-israel-regular-contact-syrian-rebels-including-isis-616404 |title=UN Report: Israel in Regular Contact with Syrian Rebels including ISIS |author=Johnlee Abraham Varghese |date=2014-12-07 |publisher=International Business Times |accessdate=2017-01-19 |archive-date=2018-05-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180516074147/https://www.ibtimes.co.in/un-report-israel-regular-contact-syrian-rebels-including-isis-616404 |dead-url=no }}</ref>以色列单方面划了红线，禁止內戰期間把先進武器移交[[黎巴嫩|黎巴嫩]][[真主黨|真主黨]]，因为这将使以军失去绝对优势。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.foxnews.com/world/2013/05/04/israel-enforces-red-line-with-syria-airstrike-on-weapons-bound-for-hezbollah/ |title=Israel enforces 'red line' with Syria airstrike on weapons bound for Hezbollah, officials say |accessdate=2013-05-07 |archive-date=2013-05-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130508001148/http://www.foxnews.com/world/2013/05/04/israel-enforces-red-line-with-syria-airstrike-on-weapons-bound-for-hezbollah/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>随着伊朗介入叙利亚，以色列又多次轰炸伊朗在叙军事目标<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/world/2019-01/21/c_1124019579.htm |title=叙利亚军方说以色列对叙发动导弹袭击 |accessdate=2019-01-21 |archive-date=2019-01-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190121232433/http://www.xinhuanet.com/world/2019-01/21/c_1124019579.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2013年1月30日，約10架以色列戰機轟炸了前往黎巴嫩的車隊，美国官员称该車隊載有俄國造的[[SA-17|SA-17]]防空導彈。敘利亞沒有進行還擊，但写信给联合国声明有自卫的權利并谴责以色列的轰炸行动。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2013/02/01/world/middleeast/syrias-confirmation-of-airstrike-may-undercut-israels-strategy-of-silence.html |title=Syria Says It Has Right to Counterattack Israel |accessdate=2013-05-07 |archive-date=2013-05-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130515124548/http://www.nytimes.com/2013/02/01/world/middleeast/syrias-confirmation-of-airstrike-may-undercut-israels-strategy-of-silence.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>根據西方情報來源，[[伊朗|伊朗]]少將{{en-link|哈山·沙特尔|Hassan Shateri}}在空襲當中喪生。伊朗確認了他遭以色列襲擊遇害的消息，并称国家将展开复仇。<ref>{{Cite web |title=Israel on global alert after killing Iran’s fox |url=http://www.thesundaytimes.co.uk/sto/news/world_news/Middle_East/article1220354.ece |accessdate=2013-05-06 |date=2013-02-24 |language=en |archive-date=2016-05-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160530180047/http://www.thesundaytimes.co.uk/sto/news/world_news/Middle_East/article1220354.ece |dead-url=no }}</ref>

多個新聞組織報導，在2013年5月2至3日的晚上，以色列再次襲擊了敘利亞。以色列拒絕回應，但一位不願意透露姓名的美國官員表示目標有可能是一處武器庫。美國政府人員稱，以色列的戰機是從黎巴嫩上空射進敘利亞的，戰機未有進入敘利亞的空域。敘利亞沒有還擊。黎巴嫩總統[[米歇爾·蘇萊曼|米歇爾·蘇萊曼]]譴責以色列使用黎巴嫩空域，並指責以方違反國際法。<ref>{{Cite web |title=Israeli warplanes 'launch air strike inside Syria' |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-22409380 |date=2013-05-04 |publisher=BBC News |accessdate=2013-05-07 |archive-date=2018-12-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181206123138/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-22409380 |dead-url=no }}</ref>5月4日，某匿名來源稱受襲的目標為運往真主黨的長程[[地對地導彈|地對地導彈]]。<ref>{{Cite web |title=Israeli Strike on Syria Targeted Weapons Shipment |url=http://abcnews.go.com/International/wireStory/israel-officials-strike-syria-targeted-weapons-19107954#.UYTeRqDLVk8 |date=2013-05-04 |publisher=ABC news |accessdate=2013-05-07 |archive-date=2013-05-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130507114604/http://abcnews.go.com/International/wireStory/israel-officials-strike-syria-targeted-weapons-19107954#.UYTeRqDLVk8 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

有新聞報導在5月4日晚上，[[大馬士革|大馬士革]]發生一連串的大規模爆炸。敘利亞官方媒體稱這次襲擊為來自以色列的火箭襲擊，受襲目標包括{{en-link|詹拉亞|Jamraya}}的一所軍方研究中心。<ref>{{Cite web |title='Israel rockets' hit Jamraya facility in Damascus |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-22417482 |accessdate=2013-05-05 |date=2013-05-05 |publisher=BBC News |archive-date=2019-04-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190426060408/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-22417482 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=Israel Targeted Iranian Missiles in Syria Attack |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2013/05/05/world/middleeast/israel-syria.html |accessdate=2013-05-05 |author=ANNE BARNARD, MICHAEL R. GORDON and JODI RUDOREN |date=2013-05-04 |publisher=New York Times |archive-date=2019-04-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190415104019/https://www.nytimes.com/2013/05/05/world/middleeast/israel-syria.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>《每日電訊報》引述以色列來源，確認了這次的空袭行动。另外根据某匿名來源，空袭目标是送往真主黨的伊朗造導彈。<ref>{{Cite web |title=Israel confirms overnight airstrikes against Damascus |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/middleeast/israel/10038315/Israel-confirms-overnight-airstrikes-against-Damascus.html |accessdate=2013-05-05 |author=Damien McElroy and agencies |date=2013-05-05 |publisher=Daily Telegraph |archive-date=2013-05-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130508121646/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/middleeast/israel/10038315/Israel-confirms-overnight-airstrikes-against-Damascus.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>位於[[英國|英國]]的親反對派觀察組織{{en-link|叙利亚人权观察站|Syrian Observatory for Human Rights}}稱，空襲中至少有42名敘利亞軍人喪生，另有100人失蹤。另一反對派來源稱死亡人數有300人，大部分都屬於[[敘利亞共和國衛隊|敘利亞共和國衛隊]]。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.jpost.com/Middle-East/No-winds-of-war-despite-alleged-Syria-air-strikes-312290 |title='No winds of war' despite Damascus air strikes |date=2013-05-07 |newspaper=Jerusalem Post |accessdate=2013-05-07 |archive-date=2013-05-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130507204435/http://www.jpost.com/Middle-East/No-winds-of-war-despite-alleged-Syria-air-strikes-312290 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

美國總統[[奧巴馬|奧巴馬]]拒絕對此次空襲回應，但重申以色列有權防止先进武器落入真主黨的手中；<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.timesofisrael.com/obama-israel-has-right-to-defend-itself-from-hezbollah/ |title=Obama: Israel has right to defend itself from Hezbollah |date=2013-05-04 |newspaper=[[Times_of_Israel|Times of Israel]] |accessdate=2013-05-05 |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303205529/http://www.timesofisrael.com/obama-israel-has-right-to-defend-itself-from-hezbollah/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>英國外交大臣[[夏偉林|夏偉林]]持相同立場。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/middleeast/syria/10038635/Syria-air-strike-Israel-has-the-right-to-defend-itself-says-William-Hague.html |title=Syria air strike: Israel has the right to defend itself, says William Hague |date=2013-05-05 |newspaper=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] |accessdate=2013-05-05 |archive-date=2018-11-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181125142347/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/middleeast/syria/10038635/Syria-air-strike-Israel-has-the-right-to-defend-itself-says-William-Hague.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>[[埃及|埃及]]總統[[穆罕默德·穆爾西|穆罕默德·穆爾西]]譴責這次空襲，並稱這會「使叙利亚内战更加複雜」。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.foxnews.com/world/2013/05/05/egypt-condemns-israeli-airstrikes-against-syria-warns-complicate-ongoing-civil/ |title=Egypt condemns Israeli airstrikes against Syria, warns they complicate ongoing civil war |date=2013-05-05 |newspaper=[[Fox_News|Fox News]] |accessdate=2013-05-05 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924182516/http://www.foxnews.com/world/2013/05/05/egypt-condemns-israeli-airstrikes-against-syria-warns-complicate-ongoing-civil/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2017年1月13日，以色列在提比利亚地区对大马士革以西的Mezzeh军事机场发射几枚导弹，导致机场被轰炸后发生大型火灾和一个重要军事设施损毁。<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.rt.com/news/373522-syria-army-base-bombed-israel/ |title=Syrian Army warns Israel it will respond after military airport bombed near Damascus (VIDEO) |date=2017-01-13 |publisher=Russia Today |accessdate=2017-01-19 |archive-date=2017-01-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170118222058/https://www.rt.com/news/373522-syria-army-base-bombed-israel/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://wearechange.org/israel-bombs-syrian-airport/ |title=Israel Bombs Syrian Airport; Syrian Army Warns of Retaliation |author=Aaron Kesel |date=2017-01-12 |publisher=wearechange.org |accessdate=2017-01-19 |archive-date=2017-01-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170117135125/http://wearechange.org/israel-bombs-syrian-airport/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>以色列官方拒绝对事件回应。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://jewishweek.timesofisrael.com/israel-bombed-military-airport-near-damascus-syrian-officials-say/ |title=Israel Bombed Military Airport Near Damascus, Syrian Officials Say |date=2017-01-13 |publisher=timesofisrael.com |accessdate=2017-01-19 |archive-date=2017-01-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170118164256/http://jewishweek.timesofisrael.com/israel-bombed-military-airport-near-damascus-syrian-officials-say/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>根据叙利亚官方，以色列这次袭击是为恐怖组织提振士气，<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://sana.sy/en/?p=98200 |title=New Israeli missile attack on Mezzeh military airport west of Damascus |date=2017-01-13 |publisher=Syrian Arab News Agency |accessdate=2017-01-19 |archive-date=2017-01-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170119224919/http://sana.sy/en/?p=98200 |dead-url=no }}</ref>因为以色列每次袭击都恰好是恐怖组织打败仗之后。叙国外交部重申，国际社会和联合国必须立即采取行动惩罚以色列侵略者，只有这样才能有效阻止以色列支持恐怖组织和不断袭击叙利亚。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://sana.sy/en/?p=98228 |title=Foreign Ministry: Israeli aggressor must be punished and prevented from repeating attacks on Syria |date=2017-01-13 |publisher=Syrian Arab News Agency |accessdate=2017-01-19 |archive-date=2017-01-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170119225036/http://sana.sy/en/?p=98228 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2018年12月25日夜间，以军控制下的[[戈兰高地|戈兰高地]]遭到数枚导弹袭击，以色列[[铁穹防御系统|铁穹防空导弹系统]]随即展开拦截，成功拦下了从叙利亚境内发射的数枚导弹，因此并未造成任何人员以及财产损失。与此同时，在遭遇袭击的后第一时间以色列空军紧急出动，再次针对叙利亚首都大马士革西部地区发动空袭。叙利亚防空导弹部队在以色列空袭过程中动用了导弹防御系统，成功拦截了以色列军机绝大多数导弹。但是此次空袭行动依旧造成3名叙军受伤，以及大马士革西部地区一所弹药库受损<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.sohu.com/a/284679348_99893142 |title=伊朗夜袭戈兰高地？以色列持续轰炸大马士革：伊朗运输机仓皇逃命  |access-date=2019-01-21 |archive-date=2022-03-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220320124718/https://www.sohu.com/a/284679348_99893142 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

